<p>
	The V.I.C.E. (Vaultopic Item Crafting Entity) will let you pull items from nearby inventories into a portable crafting table, with JEI integration.
</p>
<iframe width="1120" height="630" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IJDjj11Fsbc" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
<br>
<br>
<br>

That said, the performance cost is exclusively in the moment you click the JEI plus button.
I don't see it impacting the server a whole lot, but if any performance issues arrive, they will be looked at :)
The mod was just created and released, not a whole lot of testing yet, hopefully someone will help me with that?
The item itself does not hold any items, if you have space on your inventory when you close it the items that are still in the crafting space will go there, otherwise they'll be droped
It has shift click functionality and it will also use any items still in the crafting space if it needs them.
It will also use the items from the inventory first, and only then search nearby inventories

Both the range is configurable, and the bigger the range the higher performance cost.

